data.description: Great Home in Hesperia! This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Spacious and open kitchen newly remodeled with New kitchen cabinets, wine rack, Pantry and new Granite countertops and Island, new recessed lighting, and includes new microwave. Brand new tile flooring in kitchen and family room. Large Fireplace to enjoy on those cool or snowy evenings. Large formal living room area with tiled flooring. Fresh interior two tone paint. Huge attached enclosed patio can be used for entertaining or as a large 5th Guest bedroom, This home features a front courtyard to sit and relax with a cup of coffee and your morning paper. Large back yard also includes a shed/workshop. Front yard features plenty of RV parking and a brand new decorative Wrought Iron fence that perfectly frames in the front yard. This home is perfect for a large family and for entertaining. Take a look, you will not be disappointed.
